# 05 - Multi-Tenancy (Cloud Plugin)

> **Status:** Deferred to `dart_desk_cloud` plugin. These tests require multi-tenant support which has been extracted from the core.

The multi-tenancy E2E tests (client isolation, cross-client access, same slug for different clients) will be implemented as part of the `dart_desk_cloud` package which adds the `Tenant` model and `CloudTenantResolver`.

See: `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-03-21-multi-tenancy-extraction-design.md`
